            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>士開(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5324-TW</a>)16日09:14上漲1.05元，股價漲停報11.85元，委買3,000張、委賣38,000張，成交377張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為住宅及大樓開發租售業。都市更新重建業。不動產買賣租賃業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>士開(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5324-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲0.47%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.34%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+12 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+12 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
